{"tid":336100,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"AVAST宣布收購CCLEANER母公司-PIRIFORM","createTime":"2017-07-26T06:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T02:46:33.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d3c603d38321b24d4bcf5ecd44f655ac3dbee995","tid":336100,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:45:39.000Z","msg":"AVAST宣布，全額收購Piriform。知道此家倫敦公司的人可能不多，但正是其開發了鼎鼎大名之系統維護軟體 - CCleaner。在Windows XP / Windows 7時代，CCleaner甚至被全球眾多使用者推崇為平台最佳維護軟體。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.xfastest.com/data/attachment/forum/201707/20/121736ftmyn8yt7ebperyn.jpg.thumb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xfastest.com%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201707%2F20%2F121736ftmyn8yt7ebperyn.jpg.thumb.jpg&h=ba34df3b&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.xfastest.com/avast/38388/avast-acquisition-piriform-ccleaner/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Favast%2F38388%2Favast-acquisition-piriform-ccleaner%2F&d=KpYxcfbBRDrKVsFuHxlYx0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=53fed03e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.xfastest.com/avast/38388/avast-acquisition-piriform-ccleaner/</a>"},{"pid":"c3de75f6b9cb80d90f633dd2678581dbb6f15d1b","tid":336100,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T11:47:42.000Z","msg":"我有用CCleaner, 的確好好用, 尤其一啲連Windows XP個Add/Remove Program都uninstall唔到嘅software, 但而家好多software已經唔support XP, 部XP已經冇乜嘢可以新裝/update了, 所以CCleaner已經好少用了! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW, 仲用緊Avast係部XP度, so far so good! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef46a15c7e3f293b8b807b630f8df3c8a058b7f1","tid":336100,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:28:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c977f77146663387775b6849538